OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777165389
OL,3,CFalklands sovereignty 'not in
OL,4,Cquestion' amid fears over US stance,
OL,5,CNo 10 says
OL,7,FThe UK's position on the Falkland
OL,8,FIslands "isn't going to change",
OL,9,FDowning Street has said, amid reports
OL,10,Fthat the US could review its support
OL,11,Fof Britain's claim to the territory.
OL,13,FA leaked internal Pentagon memo
OL,14,Fsuggests the US is mulling a number of
OL,15,Fways to punish Nato members for
OL,16,Ffailing to support its operations in
OL,17,Fthe Iran war, according to a report by
OL,18,Fthe Reuters news agency.
OL,26,@pD@IOUpD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
