PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777165389
OL,3,CFalklands sovereignty 'not in
OL,4,Cquestion' amid fears over US stance,
OL,5,CNo 10 says
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Falkland
OL,8,FIslands' government told ITV News:
OL,9,F"Self-determination is a fundamental
OL,10,Fhuman right enshrined in article one,
OL,11,Fparagraph two of the Charter of the
OL,12,FUnited Nations.
OL,14,F"In 2013, the Falkland Islands held an
OL,15,Finternationally observed sovereignty
OL,16,Freferendum, in which 99.8 per cent of
OL,17,Fvoters, on a turnout of 92 per cent,
OL,18,Fvoted in favour of remaining an
OL,19,Foverseas territory of the United
OL,20,FKingdom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777165389
OL,3,CFalklands sovereignty 'not in
OL,4,Cquestion' amid fears over US stance,
OL,5,CNo 10 says
OL,7,F"The Falkland Islands has complete
OL,8,Fconfidence in the commitment made by
OL,9,Fthe UK government to uphold and defend
OL,10,Four right of self-determination."
OL,12,FConservative Party leader Kemi
OL,13,FBadenoch compared suggestions of the
OL,14,FUS dropping its support for British
OL,15,Fsovereignty over the Falklands to the
OL,16,FTrump administration's comments about
OL,17,Fannexing Greenland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777165389
OL,3,CFalklands sovereignty 'not in
OL,4,Cquestion' amid fears over US stance,
OL,5,CNo 10 says
OL,7,F"I think this is absolute nonsense,"
OL,8,Fshe told broadcasters during a visit
OL,9,Fto Swindon. "The Falkland Islands are
OL,10,FBritish, they have been for a very
OL,11,Flong time. The sovereignty is British
OL,12,Fsovereignty."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FIt comes as King Charles III and Queen
OL,20,FCamilla prepare to visit the US on
OL,21,FMonday next week.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@MOU
