PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777165389
OL,3,CFalklands sovereignty 'not in
OL,4,Cquestion' amid fears over US stance,
OL,5,CNo 10 says
OL,7,FThe four-day trip presents a potential
OL,8,Fopportunity to heal ties between
OL,9,FBritain and the United States at a
OL,10,Ftime of strained relations between
OL,11,FTrump and Starmer over his reluctance
OL,12,Fto get involved in the Iran war.
OL,14,FDespite recent tensions, the prime
OL,15,Fminister's official spokesman said:
OL,16,F"We are absolutely confident the state
OL,17,Fvisit will showcase the very best of
OL,18,Fthe UK-US bilateral relationship, from
OL,19,Fsecurity to our economic ties, and our
OL,20,Fpeople-to-people relationships."
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777165389
OL,3,CFalklands sovereignty 'not in
OL,4,Cquestion' amid fears over US stance,
OL,5,CNo 10 says
OL,7,FAsked if the visit could help repair
OL,8,Fstrained relations between the two
OL,9,Fcountries, he replied: "As I say, I
OL,10,Fthink it will showcase the very best
OL,11,Fof the UK-US relationship, but it will
OL,12,Funderline that this relationship is a
OL,13,Fdeep relationship that goes back
OL,14,Fdecades, and it is one that is forged
OL,15,Fin history, our people to people ties,
OL,16,Fas well as our economic, and security
OL,17,Fand defence relationship."
OL,26,@qD@XOUyD@ZO]
