OL,3,CFalklands sovereignty 'not in
OL,4,Cquestion' amid fears over US stance,
OL,5,CNo 10 says
OL,7,FThe spokesman indicated that the
OL,8,Fgovernment supported Spain remaining a
OL,9,FNato member. He added that the Nato
OL,10,Falliance was "an absolutely critical
OL,11,Falliance".
OL,13,FHe told reporters: "It is keeping
OL,14,FBritish people safe, people across
OL,15,FEurope safe, and it remains a core
OL,16,Fpart of our defence and in fact co-
OL,17,Foperation."
OL,26,@rD@NOUsD@IO]uD@TOUyD@KO]
